# Example api requests

## Media resource

### Get all media
GET http://localhost:3000/api/media

### Get a media item based on id
GET http://localhost:3000/api/media/9632?format=plain

### 2nd version
GET http://localhost:3000/api/media/9633
### test not found
GET http://localhost:3000/api/media/963

### Create an item
POST http://localhost:3000/api/media
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "filename": "uusi.jpg",
    "filesize": 887574,
    "title": "Uusi kuva1",
    "description": "testikuvaus",
    "user_id": 1606,
    "media_type": "image/jpeg",
    "created_at": "2023-10-16T19:00:09.000Z"
}

### Update an item
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/media/9632
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "media_id": 9632,
    "filename": "uusi.jpg",
    "filesize": 887574,
    "title": "Uusi kuva2",
    "description": "testikuvaus",
    "user_id": 1606,
    "media_type": "image/jpeg",
    "created_at": "2023-10-16T19:00:09.000Z"
}

### Delete an item
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/media/9632